No. 386,

Misc.

Sims v. Gardner, Secretary of Health, Education, and Welfare. H. H. Gearinger on the motion.

C. A. 6th Cir. Motion to consolidate this case with Hopkins v. Gardner, Secretary of Health, Education, and Welfare, No. 276 (see ante, p. 811), denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.

[For earlier order herein, see ante, p. 804.]
